And again, I don't claim ownership to the data.  I claim ownership to the right to access that data.  That right is what is in contention here.<br>
<br>
Here's a metaphor.   I buy a ticket to a baseball game.  I now have a right to access that football game.  I am allowed to sell that right to another person as long as I don't exceed the face value of the ticket.   I don't own the players, I don't own the stadium, but I do own the right to be there and the right to consume what's there(i.e. game)<br>
<br>
-Mal<br>
